import folium 

geo_df = bike_move_df
map = folium.Map(location=[geo_df[''].mean(), geo_df[''].mean()], zoom_start=12, tiles='Stamen Toner')

for n in geo_df.index:
    if geo_df.loc[n, ''] > 0 and geo_df.loc[n, ''] > 0 :
        loc_name = geo_df.loc[n, '']

        icon_color = 'red'
        folium.Circle(
            location=[geo_df.loc[n, ''], geo_df.loc[n, '']],
            popup=loc_name,
            radius=50,
            color=icon_color,
            fill=True,
            fill_color=icon_color
        ).add_to(map)
